--

Subscribe now to keep up with the best of WILD - it's past, present and future. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/WildFMYT

WILD first began as a test FM radio station in Sydney & changed the culture of dance & popular music across Australia; inspiring a new breed of club goers & music fans nationwide. 

WILD was about the vibe, the music, the energy. It inspired a series of ongoing chart-topping CD compilations that still continue today, eventually becoming one of the longest running and most recognised dance music brands in the world.
